# Which Algorithm Should You Choose?

| Use Case                        | Recommended Algorithm  |
| ------------------------------- | ---------------------- |
| API Gateways                    | Token Bucket           |
| Login & OTP Systems             | Fixed Window           |
| Network Traffic Shaping         | Leaky Bucket           |
| High-Accuracy Rate Limiting     | Sliding Window Log     |
| Large-Scale Distributed Systems | Sliding Window Counter |

